    "description": "FactoryCapi is a factory game. It's a genre of games where players manage and optimize various types of factories or production facilities.<br><br>However, FactoryCapi stands out by emphasizing two things: multiplayer interaction and offline progression.<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>In FactoryCapi, most items can be bought or sold, with very few exceptions. The item recipe tree is extensive, encouraging players to buy items they don't want to produce.<br></li><li>Your factory will be entirely running when you are offline. It is <strong>NOT</strong> just a throughput approximation; you will find your factory in the exact same state as if you stayed online (isn't it awesome?).</li></ul><br>With in-game money, you can become rich by producing and selling items in demand.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025660/extras/a3dc0740f8117c6f521ec9a0244a47a6.avif?t=1724784980\" width=670 height=498 /></span><br><br>Your progression will be shared across available platforms. During the first season, you will be able to play on Linux, Windows, and Android.<br><br>If you would like more information on the game and its features, you can read the official website.",
